54
00:03:10,540 --> 00:03:12,130
<font face="Swis721 BT" size="48"><b>¡Ves? Lo entiendes.</b></font>

55
00:03:12,130 --> 00:03:14,710
<font face="Swis721 BT" size="48"><b>El Séptimo Escuadrón te necesita.</b></font>

56
00:03:14,710 --> 00:03:16,460
<font face="Swis721 BT" size="48"><b>Pero como le dije a Tenka...</b></font>

57
00:03:16,460 --> 00:03:19,170
