<font face="Swis721 BT" size="48"><b>¡Himarin, has perdido peso!</b></font>

62
00:03:30,670 --> 00:03:31,380
<font face="Swis721 BT" size="48"><b>¿De verdad?</b></font>

63
00:03:31,380 --> 00:03:32,630
<font face="Swis721 BT" size="48"><b>Vamos, déjame apretarte un poco.</b></font>

64
00:03:32,210 --> 00:03:34,630
<font face="DomCasual BT" size="48"><b>Baño en progreso</b></font>

65
00:03:32,210 --> 00:03:34,630
<font face="DomCasual BT" size="48"><b>¡No se permiten chicos!</b></font>

66
00:03:32,210 --> 00:03:34,630
<font face="DomCasual BT" size="48"><b>¡Quédate en tu habitación!</b></font>

67
00:03:32,630 --> 00:03:33,630
